1
00:00:35,940 --> 00:00:38,820
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:41,220
=Episode 1=

3
00:00:47,740 --> 00:00:50,300
(Shen Bingfan, the greatest female
bounty hunter in the martial world)

4
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:52,679
(This is the legendary Northern Bureau.)

5
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:55,119
(Northern Bureau)
(My father's betrayer works there.)

6
00:00:55,679 --> 00:00:57,159
(I will definitely join the Jinyiwei)

7
00:00:58,119 --> 00:00:59,560
(and avenge my father.)

8
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:02,759
Is this where women sign up?

9
00:01:03,040 --> 00:01:03,640
(Xu Duoyu, a servant at Northern Bureau)

10
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:04,519
(Xu Duoyu, a servant at Northern Bureau)
Are you here to apply?

11
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,599
The Sixi Troupe's leading star is here!

12
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:09,200
Where?

13
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:10,159
The top star performer!

14
00:01:15,239 --> 00:01:16,280
She's stunning!

15
00:01:16,719 --> 00:01:17,680
Like a goddess!

16
00:01:19,140 --> 00:01:21,540
(Hua Mange,
leading star of the Sixi Opera Troupe)

17
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:25,519
Impressive!

18
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,200
Hey there.

19
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:29,160
(Female Jinyiwei Recruitment)

20
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:31,159
Do I sign up here?

21
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:33,159
Are you here for recruitment too?

22
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:35,239
Anyone else too?

23
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:43,280
(Zhang Weimin,
Commander of Northern Bureau)

24
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,480
Good. Good.

25
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:45,719
My lords.

26
00:01:46,439 --> 00:01:48,400
I am Hua Mange,

27
00:01:49,319 --> 00:01:52,159
former leading star of the Sixi Troupe.

28
00:01:53,159 --> 00:01:54,799
A few days ago,

29
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:57,079
a new girl joined our troupe

30
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,680
(Lu Guokai, Commissioner)
and took my top spot.

31
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:02,920
I had nowhere left to go...

32
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:05,040
Poor girl...

33
00:02:05,519 --> 00:02:06,000
My lord.

34
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:07,760
Your manners, please.

35
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,039
And you?

36
00:02:13,919 --> 00:02:15,080
I am Shen Bingfan.

37
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,919
I've practiced martial arts since I was young

38
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:18,360
and want to serve the court
as a Jinyiwei.

39
00:02:18,759 --> 00:02:19,560
I heard

40
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,639
you're recruiting women.

41
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:21,439
So I came.

42
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:22,680
My lord,

43
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,520
she's actually decent.

44
00:02:26,439 --> 00:02:28,039
Shen Bingfan?

45
00:02:28,879 --> 00:02:30,280
Are you the female bounty hunter

46
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:32,120
feared across the martial world?

47
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:36,319
Hey, handsome.

48
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,800
What's your name?

49
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:41,199
I'm Xu Duoyu, a Northern Bureau servant.

50
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,039
So you're not a Jinyiwei?

51
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,639
I've been here for ages,

52
00:02:46,039 --> 00:02:48,039
but never passed the physical test.

53
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,240
So I'm just a servant.

54
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:51,039
I'm grateful my lord took me in,

55
00:02:51,479 --> 00:02:53,680
so I could stay here, even as a servant.

56
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:55,360
Xu Duoyu?

57
00:02:55,919 --> 00:02:58,000
Then you'd better stay away from me.

58
00:02:58,840 --> 00:02:59,560
Why?

59
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:01,199
Because...

60
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,439
My animal sign is "cat".

61
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,199
You look like a fish.

62
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,199
(Cat?)

63
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:09,879
Duoyu.

64
00:03:10,199 --> 00:03:11,439
Where is this place?

65
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,280
Here?

66
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,759
This is the North Bureau's archive room.

67
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:15,280
It holds

68
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:17,719
(Archives)
the most complete criminal case files.

69
00:03:18,199 --> 00:03:19,560
(Archives)
It's a top-class classified division.

70
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,120
(This is where I can dig into)

71
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,360
(my father's wrongful case.)

72
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,319
(Northern Bureau)
Commander has already

73
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:30,280
(Northern Bureau)
arranged your lodging and meals.

74
00:03:30,599 --> 00:03:32,199
(Northern Bureau)
Please go across to Chong'er Pavilion.

75
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,639
Chong'er Pavilion?

76
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:34,840
It is

77
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:37,080
(Chong'er Pavilion)
among the capital's top establishments.

78
00:03:37,319 --> 00:03:38,120
So what?

79
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:40,599
You'll see when you get there.

80
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:44,080
Remember to report for duty tomorrow.

81
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:45,199
I won't see you out.

82
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:54,919
(Chang Le, Chong'er Pavilion attendant)
Meal or lodging?

83
00:03:56,159 --> 00:03:56,960
Sir.

84
00:03:57,439 --> 00:03:58,360
We're from the North Bureau...

85
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:58,800
Help!

86
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,800
- Stop!

87
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:01,159
Help!

88
00:04:01,159 --> 00:04:01,639
Get her!

89
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:03,960
Go away!

90
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,400
Don't come closer!

91
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,360
Come here!

92
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:07,479
Stop!

93
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:10,439
What are you all doing?

94
00:04:10,759 --> 00:04:11,560
A group of men bullying a woman?

95
00:04:12,759 --> 00:04:14,360
How did you get mixed up with them?

96
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:16,199
My name is Cheng Xintian.

97
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,879
(Cheng Xintian)
My mother died when I was little.

98
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,360
(Cheng Xintian)
Then my father remarried.

99
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,879
My stepmother treated me like dirt.

100
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:22,000
She beat me all the time.

101
00:04:22,399 --> 00:04:25,480
She said she'd marry me
into a rich family.

102
00:04:25,879 --> 00:04:26,360
But then...

103
00:04:26,759 --> 00:04:28,439
She meant their master,

104
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,639
an old eunuch.

105
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:31,160
Please.

106
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,560
I'm only seventeen.

107
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,199
I can't marry an old eunuch.

108
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:35,480
They...

109
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,199
They came to drag me back
for the wedding.

110
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,079
Is she telling the truth?

111
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:40,759
Her family took our master's money.

112
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:42,560
So she goes back and marries him.

113
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:45,199
Your master is a eunuch.

114
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,079
And he still wants a wife?

115
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,199
Half a man, twice the nerve.

116
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,560
How dare you!

117
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,000
She belongs to me.

118
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:53,800
I paid 500 taels for her.

119
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:54,839
You people

120
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:57,360
must have lost your minds.

121
00:04:57,879 --> 00:04:59,920
(Mr. Lü, Eastern Depot Director's aide)
How dare you cross me?

122
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,240
Try saying that again.

123
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:02,800
Our young master is here.

124
00:05:07,980 --> 00:05:09,740
(Chang Beiming,
owner of Chong'er Pavilion)

125
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:15,060
(Shizhen, son of the Minister of War)

126
00:05:16,180 --> 00:05:17,660
(Feng Zhihe,
nephew of the Eastern Depot Director)

127
00:05:17,940 --> 00:05:19,380
(Ye Ping, son of the Grand Secretary)

128
00:05:24,319 --> 00:05:25,399
Didn't I make it clear?

129
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,959
No ugly faces in my Chong'er Pavilion.

130
00:05:28,319 --> 00:05:28,680
What...

131
00:05:28,759 --> 00:05:29,759
This is our business.

132
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:31,439
No need to drag you into it.

133
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:33,920
In Chong'er Pavilion,

134
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,560
you don't get to talk.

135
00:05:37,439 --> 00:05:39,079
Someone's helping. Take the win.

136
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:42,160
Listen carefully.

137
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:43,399
She is my wife.

138
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:45,800
I bought her for 500 taels.

139
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:48,120
Take this to the Dali Temple for review

140
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:49,560
and the law is still on my side.

141
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,000
I'm not afraid of you.

142
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:52,360
What do we do?

143
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,360
He does have proof.

144
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,439
We don't have a case.

145
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,519
Then I'll buy her out.

146
00:05:59,439 --> 00:06:00,000
Fine.

147
00:06:00,079 --> 00:06:00,800
Principal and interest.

148
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,240
1,000 taels.

149
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:05,079
You only paid 500 for me.

150
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,480
Your food, your clothes,

151
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,040
everything came from me.

152
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,279
I...

153
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,639
1,000 it is.

154
00:06:14,839 --> 00:06:16,839
Good. Pay up.

155
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:28,120
Could you

156
00:06:28,639 --> 00:06:29,759
lend me one thousand taels?

157
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,040
I'll repay every coin.

158
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:32,639
You don't have the money?

159
00:06:32,639 --> 00:06:34,120
Then why agree to pay?

160
00:06:36,759 --> 00:06:38,199
When will you pay me back?

161
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,439
Within three days.

162
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,279
And if you can't?

163
00:06:41,639 --> 00:06:42,800
I'll work off the debt.

164
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:43,959
Anything?

165
00:06:43,959 --> 00:06:45,319
If it doesn't betray my conscience

166
00:06:45,319 --> 00:06:46,360
and my honor.

167
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:47,680
I like that.

168
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:49,279
Chang Le.

169
00:06:49,959 --> 00:06:50,360
Pay them off.

170
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,120
Here.

171
00:06:55,759 --> 00:06:56,600
Let's go.

172
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,160
Go. Go.

173
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:02,639
Thank you, both of you.

174
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:04,720
Mr. Chang.

175
00:07:05,319 --> 00:07:07,000
We were ordered to stay here.

176
00:07:08,519 --> 00:07:08,920
That's right.

177
00:07:09,439 --> 00:07:12,199
We're the new female Jinyiwei.

178
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:15,199
The Jinyiwei has women now?

179
00:07:17,660 --> 00:07:18,480
(Zhang Weimin)

180
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,920
Zhang Weiming.

181
00:07:21,639 --> 00:07:22,199
Chang Le.

182
00:07:22,319 --> 00:07:22,639
Yes, sir.

183
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,600
Get these ladies settled.

184
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:25,480
Check them in.

185
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:26,839
Thank you.

186
00:07:34,279 --> 00:07:34,879
Chang.

187
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:37,160
Quite a scene today.

188
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,319
Shall we settle the bill?

189
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:42,319
(Leisurely and Free)
Here at Chong'er Pavilion,

190
00:07:42,319 --> 00:07:43,519
(Leisurely and Free)
every single piece

191
00:07:43,519 --> 00:07:46,199
is either an antique
or imperial kilnware.

192
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:47,959
You know exactly

193
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:48,759
how much you broke.

194
00:07:48,879 --> 00:07:50,360
And for Miss... what was it?

195
00:07:50,519 --> 00:07:51,959
Miss Cheng.

196
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:53,199
Buying her freedom cost me...

197
00:07:53,439 --> 00:07:54,360
1,000 taels.

198
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:55,519
Yes, 1,000 taels.

199
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,319
All together,

200
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,560
that comes to...

201
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,560
Let's call it 3,000 taels.

202
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:03,319
3,000 taels?

203
00:08:04,060 --> 00:08:05,420
(Cheng Xintian)

204
00:08:05,500 --> 00:08:06,740
(Hua Mange)

205
00:08:08,380 --> 00:08:10,260
(Shen Bingfan)

206
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:13,319
All settled. Everyone out.

207
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:15,360
Miss.

208
00:08:18,639 --> 00:08:21,279
You know, you look nice when you smile.

209
00:08:33,799 --> 00:08:36,039
You can talk all you want,

210
00:08:36,279 --> 00:08:38,320
but I'm not letting you three stay here.

211
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:40,799
Seriously,

212
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,519
why did you have to hit him?

213
00:08:43,679 --> 00:08:44,840
He was harassing me.

214
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,720
How was that harassment?

215
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,360
He... he got so close to me.

216
00:08:48,759 --> 00:08:50,399
And he said things like that.

217
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:53,279
I just said you look nice smiling.

218
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,720
I don't like that.

219
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:55,960
Well, you never told me.

220
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:57,840
Miss Shen,

221
00:08:58,159 --> 00:08:59,679
allow me to be fair here.

222
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,919
Beiming may have

223
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:04,639
overstepped with his words,

224
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:07,120
but you struck him.

225
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:09,480
Wasn't that a bit much?

226
00:09:10,039 --> 00:09:10,840
Exactly.

227
00:09:12,399 --> 00:09:13,480
Young Master Chang,

228
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:15,159
she's a girl.

229
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:16,440
She's naturally sensitive.

230
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:19,840
Teasing her the first time you meet

231
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,840
can easily come off as improper.

232
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:23,120
But still,

233
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:25,639
she was wrong to hit you.

234
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:26,519
How about this?

235
00:09:26,519 --> 00:09:27,679
Both sides take a step back.

236
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,080
Shen,

237
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,519
apologize to Young Master Chang.

238
00:09:30,879 --> 00:09:32,879
Sir, be the bigger man

239
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:34,120
and let this go.

240
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,399
Beiming cares about face the most.

241
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:38,360
No one has ever dared hit him.

242
00:09:38,799 --> 00:09:40,759
Especially not in front of a crowd.

243
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:41,919
Today,

244
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,879
you really made history.

245
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,200
Guys.

246
00:09:45,639 --> 00:09:46,200
He

247
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:49,159
really can defy the Northern Bureau?

248
00:09:49,559 --> 00:09:51,720
Zhang Weimin can't afford to cross him.

249
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,120
Why not?

250
00:09:54,759 --> 00:09:57,679
Northern Bureau's in debt to him.

251
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,039
Those people

252
00:10:00,519 --> 00:10:02,720
come here all the time
and eat on credit.

253
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,639
It adds up to quite a debt in a year.

254
00:10:05,639 --> 00:10:06,480
Just apologize.

255
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,240
Don't make this worse.

256
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:09,240
Or we'll have nowhere to sleep tonight.

257
00:10:24,159 --> 00:10:26,039
If you're still angry,
you can hit me back.

258
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:32,039
You really are stubborn.

259
00:10:32,639 --> 00:10:34,440
So tell me. What do you want?

260
00:10:36,399 --> 00:10:37,720
You want to stay here

261
00:10:38,039 --> 00:10:39,759
and keep working at Northern Bureau?

262
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:41,759
Then sell yourselves to me.

263
00:10:42,519 --> 00:10:43,200
For six months,

264
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:45,080
you'll wait tables for free

265
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:47,360
and do whatever I say.

266
00:11:03,140 --> 00:11:06,310
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

267
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:10,060
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

268
00:11:10,310 --> 00:11:13,310
♪My heart drifted lost♪

269
00:11:13,310 --> 00:11:16,720
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

270
00:11:17,810 --> 00:11:21,020
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

271
00:11:21,430 --> 00:11:24,770
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

272
00:11:25,350 --> 00:11:27,560
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

273
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:31,600
♪I've softly let it go♪

274
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:35,470
♪The vow you made was true♪

275
00:11:35,470 --> 00:11:39,220
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

276
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:41,430
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

277
00:11:41,430 --> 00:11:45,970
♪And forget at world's end♪

278
00:11:46,270 --> 00:11:47,770
♪Embracing memory♪

279
00:11:47,770 --> 00:11:50,140
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

280
00:11:50,140 --> 00:11:54,020
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

281
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:56,350
♪I wish to let it pass♪

282
00:11:56,350 --> 00:12:01,350
♪And run toward this vast life♪

